# Runtime log dirs created by the plugin-manager when the e2e harness points
# ROUBO_USER_PLUGINS_DIR at e2e/fixtures/ (WU-063): logs end up at
# e2e/fixtures/<pluginId>/logs/. Pure runtime artefact, never committed.
# Covers e2e-stub, the WU-065 siblings (e2e-stub-2..5), and bundled plugins
# (github-com, ghe, jira-self-hosted) that also drop logs under this root.
e2e/fixtures/e2e-stub/
e2e/fixtures/e2e-stub-[2-9]/
e2e/fixtures/github-com/
e2e/fixtures/ghe/
e2e/fixtures/jira-self-hosted/
e2e/fixtures/broken-plugin/
